VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \.evaluateJavaScript\s*\(
WHEN EXPR MISSING:sanitize|escape|encode|htmlEncode|jsEncode|allowList|trustedScript|#\ safe
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects evaluateJavaScript calls that may execute user-controlled or unsanitized script strings.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for evaluateJavaScript with Potentially User-Controlled Input.
